# Receiver Integration Family Rules

- Apply this rule when `projectFamily` is `receiver-integration`.
- Keep ingress configuration, protocol parsing, sample payloads, publish targets, retry, and diagnostics aligned.
- Treat `Java 11 + Spring Boot 2.7.x` as the default baseline unless a documented exception exists.
- Combine this rule with the `receiver` runtime-role rule.
